Package: libmockspotify-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends:
    libmockspotify2 (= ${binary:Version}),
    ${misc:Depends},
    libspotify-dev (>= 12.0.0), libspotify-dev (<< 13)
Description: Mock of the libspotify library
 This development package provides the header files and symbolic links to allow
 compilation and linking of programs that use libmockspotify as a drop-in
 replacement for libspotify for testing.

Package: libmockspotify2
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mock of the libspotify library
 libmockspotify is a drop-in replacement for libspotify which may be used for
 testing programs depending on libspotify.
